data.description: Experience Lakeside Luxury Living at its finest with this unique custom-built Waterfront Estate. Nestled inside a gated community on a private corner lake lot with a double dock slip and 100' of shoreline lake frontage. The home boasts such opulent features as a Main Level with an expansive Open Floor Plan highlighted by a Cathedral ceiling. The expansive Great Room features a Chef’s Kitchen with its own breakfast area and dining area, SS appliances with a Butler’s pantry overlooking unmatched views of Lake Lanier through a myriad of windows. Step outside and enjoy a wraparound PVC DECK featuring a Greenhouse on the home’s south side. Your luxury resort amenities are highlighted with a 32ft by 32ft Double Slip, Deep Water Dock w/ a Party Deck. The Dock is located in a private Cove that flows into the widest part of the Lake and provides picturesque views of the rising Sun and Moon. The home’s upstairs features a private loft that is perfect for company with Three Bedrooms, a Bathroom, and a Library that overlooks the vaulted Great Room. A Finished Basement on the home’s Terrace Level, features a Workout room with a Sauna, an entertainment area with a Bar, Billiard tables, 1 Bed/ Bath, and its own Media/ Theater room with amazing lake views as well!
